title: Gossip | Watch: Instagram videos highlight how much Kim, Kylie and Khloe's faces have changed...
text:
"Is that a great message for little girls? A whole family of women who take the faces they were born with as a light suggestion?" Amy Schumer, SNL opening monologue . And yes, you did "used to have Khloe. She used to be ours..." but then this happened...
As for sister Kim, the SaintHoax instagram account captioned the below video: "Maybe she's born with it... Maybe it's a bit more than "contouring" ðŸ'‰#PumpingUpTheKardashians."
Of course, there is the youngest of them all - Kylie Jenner - who had most of her work done aged 17.
And, when you put it all together, it's a total head melt. And before anyone starts giving out - yes, their faces their choice. They just so happen to be making their choices in front of millions.
